---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import DomainGenerator from '../../components/DomainGenerator';
import SimilarTools from '../../components/SimilarTools';
---

<Layout title="AI Domain Name Generator - AI-Free-Forever">
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-50 to-orange-100/50 py-16 mb-12 rounded-2xl text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
        AI Domain Name Generator
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Generate creative and available domain names for your business using AI. Get instant suggestions that match your brand.
      </p>
    </div>
    <DomainGenerator client:load />
    
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mt-16">
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">Find the Perfect Name Instantly with Our AI Domain Name Generator – 100% Free</h2>
        <p class="text-lg mb-6">Choosing the right domain name is critical to building a strong online presence. Our AI Domain Name Generator helps you find creative, brandable, and available domain names in seconds, tailored to your business idea, niche, or project.</p>
        
        <p class="text-lg mb-8">Powered by advanced GPT-4o technology, the AI Domain Name Generator is completely free to use — no limits, no hidden fees, and no subscriptions required. Whether you're launching a startup, building a personal brand, or starting a blog, our tool gives you endless possibilities to name your next big idea.</p>
        
        <p class="text-lg mb-4">Every generated domain suggestion is:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-6">
          <li class="text-lg">Unique and memorable</li>
          <li class="text-lg">SEO-friendly</li>
          <li class="text-lg">Industry-relevant</li>
          <li class="text-lg">Instantly checkable for domain availability</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p class="text-lg mb-8">No brainstorming blocks, no tedious hours searching—just fast, smart naming ideas ready for you.</p>
        
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">How to Generate the Perfect Domain Name in 4 Easy Steps</h2>
        <p class="text-lg mb-4">Using the AI Domain Name Generator is fast, simple, and intuitive:</p>
        <ol class="list-decimal pl-6 space-y-4 mb-8">
          <li class="text-lg">
            <span class="font-semibold">Enter Keywords</span>
            <p>Provide keywords related to your brand, product, or niche to seed the AI's creativity.</p>
          </li>
          <li class="text-lg">
            <span class="font-semibold">Select Style Preferences</span>
            <p>Choose whether you want your domain name to be short, brandable, descriptive, creative, professional, or playful.</p>
          </li>
          <li class="text-lg">
            <span class="font-semibold">Add Optional Requirements</span>
            <p>Specify extensions like .com, .io, .ai, or niche-specific TLDs, and set preferences like including specific words or keeping character limits.</p>
          </li>
          <li class="text-lg">
            <span class="font-semibold">Generate and Review</span>
            <p>Click "generate" to instantly receive a list of domain ideas. Review your options, check availability, and secure your favorite.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
        
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">Why Smart Businesses Use Our AI Domain Name Generator</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Creativity Without the Guesswork</h3>
            <p>The AI Domain Name Generator produces highly creative names based on real branding best practices, so you stand out immediately.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">SEO-Friendly and Market-Ready</h3>
            <p>Names are suggested with SEO considerations in mind—giving your brand a better start in search rankings.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Domain Availability Checking</h3>
            <p>Each suggestion comes with an option to check domain availability, so you don't fall in love with an unavailable name.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Fast and Unlimited</h3>
            <p>Generate as many domain names as you need — refine, regenerate, and brainstorm until you find the perfect fit.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">Who Benefits Most From the AI Domain Name Generator?</h2>
        <p class="text-lg mb-4">Our AI Domain Name Generator is ideal for:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-8">
          <li class="text-lg"><span class="font-semibold">Startups:</span> Quickly generate brandable names that can scale with your business vision.</li>
          <li class="text-lg"><span class="font-semibold">Entrepreneurs:</span> Find premium-quality names without paying expensive naming agencies.</li>
          <li class="text-lg"><span class="font-semibold">Bloggers:</span> Create catchy, memorable blog names that attract traffic.</li>
          <li class="text-lg"><span class="font-semibold">E-Commerce Stores:</span> Find product-specific or niche brand names that convert shoppers.</li>
          <li class="text-lg"><span class="font-semibold">Content Creators:</span> Generate standout names for YouTube channels, podcasts, and personal brands.</li>
          <li class="text-lg"><span class="font-semibold">Developers and Tech Projects:</span> Get modern, tech-relevant domain names ready for your app, SaaS tool, or portfolio.</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">Tips for Choosing the Best Domain Name</h2>
        <p class="text-lg mb-4">Maximize the Power of the AI Domain Name Generator with These Tips:</p>
        <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-8">
          <table class="min-w-full bg-white rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
            <thead class="bg-gray-50">
              <tr>
                <th class="py-3 px-4 text-left text-gray-900 font-semibold">Tip</th>
                <th class="py-3 px-4 text-left text-gray-900 font-semibold">Why It Matters</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-200">
              <tr>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-900">Keep it Short and Memorable</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">Names under 15 characters are easier to remember, type, and share.</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-900">Make It Brandable</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">Unique combinations (like Spotify or Airbnb) are easier to trademark and build identity around.</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-900">Think About SEO</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">Consider including important keywords if they naturally fit without making the name too long or awkward.</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-900">Prioritize .com (If Possible)</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">While there are many TLD options today, a .com domain is still the most trusted and remembered.</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-900">Act Quickly</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">Domain names sell fast! If you love one, register it as soon as possible.</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
        
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">Frequently Asked Questions About the AI Domain Name Generator</h2>
        <div class="space-y-6 mb-8">
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Is the AI Domain Name Generator really free to use?</h3>
            <p>Yes! You can generate unlimited domain name ideas for free with no subscriptions or hidden fees.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Will the domain names be available for purchase?</h3>
            <p>Our tool provides instant availability checks for your generated names, so you can easily see what's ready to register.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Can I specify domain extensions (.com, .io, .ai)?</h3>
            <p>Absolutely! You can choose your preferred extension(s) when generating domain names.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Can I generate names for different industries?</h3>
            <p>Yes, the AI Domain Name Generator works for all industries—tech, fashion, wellness, finance, education, entertainment, and more.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Is my data secure?</h3>
            <p>Yes, we do not store your keywords, preferences, or generated lists after your session ends.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">AI Domain Name Generator vs. Paid Naming Services</h2>
        <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-8">
          <table class="min-w-full bg-white rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
            <thead class="bg-gray-50">
              <tr>
                <th class="py-3 px-4 text-left text-gray-900 font-semibold">Feature</th>
                <th class="py-3 px-4 text-left text-gray-900 font-semibold">aiFreeForever AI Domain Name Generator</th>
                <th class="py-3 px-4 text-left text-gray-900 font-semibold">Branding Agencies</th>
                <th class="py-3 px-4 text-left text-gray-900 font-semibold">Premium AI Naming Tools</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-200">
              <tr>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-900">Price</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">Always Free</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">$500–$5,000+ per project</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">$20–$100/month</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-900">Turnaround Time</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">Instant</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">1–4 weeks</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">Minutes</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-900">Creativity</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">High (AI-Powered)</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">High (Human-Crafted)</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">Medium</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-900">SEO Optimization</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">Yes</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">Sometimes</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">Rarely</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-900">Account Required</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">No</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">Yes</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">Yes</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
        
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">Launch Your Next Big Idea Today</h2>
        <p class="text-lg mb-8">Use the AI Domain Name Generator now to find the perfect, brandable domain name that sets your project up for success — all for free, with no limits, and no headaches.</p>
        
        <div class="bg-orange-50 p-6 rounded-xl text-center mb-8">
          <p class="text-lg font-semibold">👉 Start using the AI Domain Name Generator today and secure the perfect name for your online presence!</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <SimilarTools currentToolPath="domain-generator" category="writing" client:load />
  </main>
</Layout>